something about the procedures (
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

the raw data is not always fitting...
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

) and our vast experience with the data, that allows dealing with a lot
 of the weaknesses of EHR
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
something about the methodology of external validation.
 2 tests for every model, ex.
 val and comparing.
 discrimination, calibration, confusion matrix, decision curves, etc.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Something about the methodology of developing our own model, including the
 follow-up time, the outcome definitions, the use of clinical counsel, the
 different covariates (more than anyone uses), the use of ML technique (10-fold-
CV, random search, etc.), the use of ML models (LASSO, xgboost, ANNs), the
 careful testing, etc.
 Something about the use of competing risks?
\end_layout

